<p>
  <span class="nym">Altrude</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>alt</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon, Old Frisian</span> <i>ald</i> 'old' + <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*þrūþ</i> 'strength' or <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*trut</i> 'maiden'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>See also <a class="nym" href="Adaltrude">Adaltrude</a>.</p>
</div>
  


